  <brief_title>Evaluating the Use of Thromboelastography to Diagnose Coagulopathy After Traumatic Brain Injury</brief_title>
  <official_title>Evaluating the Use of Thromboelastography to Diagnose and Monitor Coagulopathy Associated With Pediatric Traumatic Brain Injury</official_title>
